* üõ°Ô∏è Configurable CORS protection
* üìù Proper UTF-8 handling for all characters
* ‚öôÔ∏è Configurable file path and limits

**Note**: The complete, production-ready code is ~280 lines. See the GitHub repository for the full implementation.
""">>

<<setup-step "4" "Set Environment Variables" """
In Cloudflare Pages ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Environment Variables ‚Üí **Production**:

